                        Make sure you complete the whole set. For a limited time only you will be able to reserve the next three Brilliant Uncirculated &pound;5 coins ahead of their official release dates:
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="variantSpecifications">
                    <div class="col-xs-12">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="">
                                <h2 class="">Specifications</h2>
                                <table class="table table-spec mb-0">
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>Spec Item</th>
                                        <td>Item Description</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>Spec Item</th>
                                        <td>Item Description</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>Spec Item</th>
                                        <td>Item Description</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>Spec Item</th>
                                        <td>Item Description</td>
